snippet.title: Schrödinger's Cat and the Raiders of the Lost Quark Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Schrödinger's Cat and the Raiders of the Lost Quark  is a platformer-puzzler-punch-up of subatomic proportions! Brought to you by Italic Pig and Team17. Visit http://www.lostquark.com and follow @italicpig for updates and awesomeness.

Schrödinger’s Cat and the Raiders of the Lost Quark is available to download for PC, Mac and Linux: http://store.steampowered.com/app/295490/.

Team17, founded in 1990, are a fully independent video game developer and publisher responsible for the Worms™ series, Alien Breed and Superfrog. Ensure you never miss out on our latest videos by subscribing to us now: http://bit.ly/SubscribeT17.

Don't forget you can also Like us on Facebook: http://bit.ly/LikeT17
Follow us on Twitter: http://bit.ly/FollowT17
